column5: Lots of smaller fish getting in the way though  Nice sunrise over calm waters    Got Bait?   Kings!             Cohos!     And a nice sunset to finish it off   Covered a lot of water in my search, hope to lock into something with some weight before the derby ends.  Tony
You'll get one Tony, I can feel it.  You've been doing well by the looks of it.  Have you entered any yet?  Joey
Lots of them little guys around. Good luck with your contender!
